{"tid":2447570,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"水定火勁d?","createTime":"2021-03-15T09:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T12:24:04.000Z","uid":10172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"02d1b765a20faa71e70cc7023c98f4a6929672dd","tid":2447570,"uid":10172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"火要點量度個量去同水去鬥？<br />\n例如1000ml水可以淋熄幾多火？"},{"pid":"39fab8012188d28e2d225f69a7d74d3b4df409e4","tid":2447570,"uid":323740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"風勁d"},{"pid":"70288996233152035ae70b8d92b468f2125bce06","tid":2447570,"uid":193770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"雷最勁"},{"pid":"24fece6374a0b1973430ea9703f8f82a45457ba2","tid":2447570,"uid":10172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"水同火比較你地答第d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b12cf64b7d32a7142d1772fe5f2963711d200bf","tid":2447570,"uid":125192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"千鳥定係雷切勁d?"},{"pid":"bb428ebcd6fe1cf2748eabfa1ff414bdb80b1dec","tid":2447570,"uid":31744,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3b12cf64b7d32a7142d1772fe5f2963711d200bf","tid":2447570,"uid":125192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"千鳥定係雷切勁d?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"千鳥同雷切最大ge分別係威力<br />\n雷切係千鳥ge進化版,,<br />\n因卡卡西用千鳥切斷咗雷電,<br />\n所以卡卡西ge千鳥就改名為雷切<br />\n而兩者都需要有寫輪眼配合,<br />\n因為呢種忍術係直線型攻擊,<br />\n容易俾敵人睇穿攻擊路線,<br />\n有寫輪眼就可以預知到敵人ge動作,<br />\n作出適當應變措施<br />\n<br />\n而點解雷切係S級忍術,千鳥係A級忍術,<br />\n原因一:結印<br />\n雷切結ge印比千鳥少,<br />\n但係威力就大過千鳥好多<br />\n原因二:速度<br />\n雷切係需要高速前衝<br />\n而千鳥就咁用長距離助跑(普通速度)就得<br />\n原因三:卓羅<br />\n雷切需要將卓羅凝聚係手掌,<br />\n卓羅量大到可以變成利刃,<br />\n連卡卡西用果時隻手會流血,<br />\n仲可以貫穿人體<br />\n千鳥一樣需要將卓羅凝聚係手掌,<br />\n不過卓羅量就冇雷切咁勁,<br />\n貫穿唔到人體<br />\n<br />\n所以雷切勁d"},{"pid":"2da980fe67f64a664e949c37d4e2b2d1a897a8b0","tid":2447570,"uid":10172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:34:09.000Z","msg":"認真問呀 點解仲未有人答到我！！！"},{"pid":"3ff101d813968a951d0c6d560ff7e21e2ea0e8c9","tid":2447570,"uid":186915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"水勁d<br />\n火災可以救熄<br />\n水災只可以等自然水退"},{"pid":"354a46239372aa17382e60a40ece73d27dd32c65","tid":2447570,"uid":10172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ff101d813968a951d0c6d560ff7e21e2ea0e8c9","tid":2447570,"uid":186915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"水勁d<br />\n火災可以救熄<br />\n水災只可以等自然水退"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"有道理 但邊個殺傷力強d?"},{"pid":"e93b98c2a955407797d3735cb7f2474617283c45","tid":2447570,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"354a46239372aa17382e60a40ece73d27dd32c65","tid":2447570,"uid":10172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ff101d813968a951d0c6d560ff7e21e2ea0e8c9","tid":2447570,"uid":186915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"水勁d<br />\n火災可以救熄<br />\n水災只可以等自然水退"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"有道理 但邊個殺傷力強d?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"火<br />\n因為水淨係會濕下身<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/treegun1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F04%2Ftreegun1.jpg&h=16d69375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fbe592409ea677fa82d5091da703c76c5140d2c","tid":2447570,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"水啦<br />\n<br />\n海嘯屈機  冇野頂得住<br />\n<br />\n火你唔理佢自然會燒晒"},{"pid":"4b68f3effa62438e930c719e89ec1bc72620c575","tid":2447570,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:5